forum.name: tips for newbies
forum.description: just started anyland? confused about what to do? these are the things i learned that i think everyone should know!
forum.latestCommentText: here is an object that you can place into your area that explains how lighting works in a nice visual aid.

thread.title: areas to show what you can do!

comments.text: there are so many things you can do in anyland, but it was hard for me to come up with ideas, so here is a collection of all the great areas i've found that have cool concepts or..
items to get ideas from. to travel to a place listed here, just touch the buttons to the right with your finger.
[body shop] - don't be a series of floating dots! get yourself a face and body.
[fazzis home] - great to explore many amazing places. touch doorknobs to go through doors.
[cafe 80s] - old style diner with some neat things in it.
